
To install RKE on a VM  (nto required because, this can be done as side step. )
 
 follow this document  - https://rancher.com/docs/rke/latest/en/installation/

       > wget https://github.com/rancher/rke/releases/download/v1.0.8/rke_linux-amd64
       > mv rke_linux-amd64 rke
       > sudo cp rke /usr/bin/
       > sudo chmod +x /usr/bin/rke
